# create-sveltex

## Creating a project

If you're seeing this, you've probably already done this step. Otherwise:

```bash
pnpm dlx create-sveltex # If using PNPM
bunx create-sveltex     # If using Bun
npx create-sveltex      # If using NPM
yarn dlx create-sveltex # If using Yarn
```

## Developing

Once you've created a project and installed dependencies, start a development
server:

```bash
pnpm run dev
```

## Building

To create a production version of your app:

```bash
pnpm run build
```

You can then preview the production build with the following:

```bash
pnpm run preview
```
