## Troubleshooting

### Husky hooks not running

Be sure to run `{{packageManager}} install` at least once _after_ initializing
your git repository to ensure that Husky's hooks are set up correctly. If that
still doesn't fix the issue, ensure that the `prepare` script in `package.json`
is `husky` or `svelte-kit sync && husky` and run `{{packageManager}} install`
again. If you're still having trouble, consult the [Husky
documentation](https://typicode.github.io/husky/troubleshoot.html).
